---

# 十五、Knowledge Graph Mapping

Relationship 默认支持：

Knowledge Graph。

例如：

```
(Customer)

↓

Purchased

↓

(Product)
```

或者：

```
(Customer)

↓

Recommended

↓

(Customer)
```

统一采用：

Subject

Predicate

Object

三元组模型。

---

# 十六、Relationship Domain Event

Relationship 变化产生事件。

例如：

```
RelationshipCreated

RelationshipUpdated

RelationshipExpired

RelationshipArchived

ReferralCreated

AdvisorAssigned

HouseholdCreated
```

Relationship 是重要事件来源。

---

# 十七、API Mapping

统一接口。

```
POST /relationships

GET /relationships

PUT /relationships/{id}

DELETE /relationships/{id}
```

Relationship 统一管理。

禁止：

直接修改外键。

---

# 十八、AI Semantic Mapping

AI 默认理解：

```
Customer

↓

Relationship

↓

Graph
```

例如：

```
Customer

↓

Friend

↓

VIP Customer
```

AI 可进行：

- 推荐
- 推理
- 社交分析
- 客户网络分析
- 推荐链分析

---

# 十九、Relationship Registry

JBOS 建议建立：

```
Relationship Registry

Customer

↓

Customer

↓

RelationshipType

↓

Business Meaning

↓

Lifecycle

↓

Owner Domain
```

统一管理所有关系。

---

# 二十、Business Relationship Matrix（业务关系矩阵）

| Source | Relationship | Target | Owner |
|----------|-------------|---------|--------|
| Customer | BelongsTo | Household | Customer |
| Customer | AdvisedBy | Advisor | Customer |
| Customer | Holds | Membership | Customer |
| Customer | Purchased | Product | Sales |
| Customer | Places | Order | Sales |
| Customer | Visits | Store | Store |
| Customer | Participates | Campaign | Marketing |
| Customer | Receives | AI Recommendation | AI |

Relationship 的 Owner 决定维护责任。

---

# 二十一、未来演进

Relationship 将逐步发展为：

```text
Relationship

↓

Business Graph

↓

Knowledge Graph

↓

Customer Graph

↓

Enterprise Graph

↓

Digital Twin Graph

↓

Autonomous Business Graph
```

最终：

JBOS 不再管理数据。

而是管理：

企业经营关系网络。

---

# 二十二、本章总结

Relationship 是 JBOS Customer Domain 的核心能力之一。

Customer 不再是静态资料，而是经营网络中的核心节点。

JBOS 通过统一 Relationship Model，将客户、商品、门店、订单、会员、导购、社区及 AI 全部连接到统一的 Business Relationship Graph 中。

未来，Relationship 将进一步演进为企业知识图谱（Knowledge Graph）和 AI 智能推理网络，为客户经营、精准营销、智能推荐、AI Agent 协同及数字孪生提供统一的关系基础。

